snippet: On Saturday, Donald J. Trump returned to Alabama, to the site of a campaign rally 16 months ago that lifted his campaign’s confidence during a time he was still being dismissed in the primary race....
abstract: Pres-elect Donald J Trump ends his so-called thank you tour with self-congratulatory speech at 40,000-seat Ladd-Peebles Stadium in Mobile, Ala, where his campaign first began to gain serious traction and higher profile.
lead_paragraph: On Saturday, Donald J. Trump returned to Alabama, to the site of a campaign rally 16 months ago that lifted his campaign’s confidence during a time he was still being dismissed in the primary race.

headline.main: Trump Ends ‘Thank You’ Tour on Familiar Theme: Reveling in His Victory
headline.print_headline: Trump Ends ‘Thank You’ Tour on Familiar Theme: Reveling in His Win
